{"tid":2210103,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"點解套戲會唔好睇 原來係少咗...","createTime":"2020-09-20T07:03:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T09:20:10.000Z","uid":326043,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"22c3c7b3216b7f1a937fba61f585d726e24458b7","tid":2210103,"uid":326043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T07:03:33.000Z","msg":"係時間<br />\n少咗嘅係時間啊<br />\n<br />\n講緊嘅係集數/季 之間嘅時間<br />\n第一集同第二集之間距離越耐越好睇<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0SzDAby.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0SzDAby.jpg&h=5236e72c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIndependence day <br />\n(第一集同第二集之間隔左成廿年)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j303Mjd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj303Mjd.jpg&h=e2ee52f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nStar Wars 系列<br />\n(三集三集咁出 第一集同第九集隔左廿年)<br />\n<br />\n發覺無論喺NETFLIX睇電影定劇集<br />\n都係要慢慢Dap先至好睇 <br />\n第一集 第二集之間<br />\n第一季 第二季之間 隔翻三幾個月先再追下一季 <br />\n咁先至可以真正體驗到套劇同電影<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GzEj341.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGzEj341.jpg&h=52a40611&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMarvel美國隊長123<br />\n如果你係睇avg4前先一次過追曬marvel 啲戲嘅忽然fans<br />\n就會心諗條友jm9<br />\n集集都repeat: I can do this all day<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kX1OcYs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkX1OcYs.png&h=b48da571&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又或者係friends 最後幾季<br />\n好鐘意將早幾季啲回憶片段剪剪埋埋一集<br />\n如果你係睇咗十年嘅老觀眾<br />\n就好多回憶 睇到眼濕濕 <br />\n但係如果你係武肺先開始煲<br />\n明明嗰集上個禮拜先睇完 就會睇到好悶<br />\n<br />\n結論：<br />\n套戲一出就已經睇緊嘅人已成人生贏家<br />\n最近先睇就同一時間煲幾套戲 比啲時間自己冷靜吓 <br />\n沉澱一排 先再睇下一季<br />\n再睇翻見到啲致敬嘅場面自然會會心微笑"},{"pid":"a0dcd6b8bae227b86c9d93bba0e9d23767697386","tid":2210103,"uid":326043,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"22c3c7b3216b7f1a937fba61f585d726e24458b7","tid":2210103,"uid":326043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"